// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1363 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: f32415a6-7832-5df0-977a-0a55244c12b7

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*")
